name: Chadra-Fan
Lore: 'Short, intelligent and selfish. Their enhanced vision and smell make them outstanding Thieves. Communicate with pheromones and high-pitched squeaks.',
Text: 'Power and forfeit +2 while Kabe at Audience Chamber. During your control phase, may glance at one card randomly selected from opponent''s hand; if that card is a character weapon, may ''steal'' it into your hand.',
